Requirements:
 Python 2.4+ (Python 2.3 untested)
 MySQL Python module
 imagemagick's convert command

Installation:
 Download and extract the latest release ZIP file in a directory with some method of executing Python as a web application (FastCGI is highly recommended)
 Ensure the first line of pyib.py is the path to the Python binary you wish to use
 Edit Settings.py
 CHMOD pyib.py to allow execution
 Import the pyib.sql file to the configured database
 Go to http://your.installation.url.com/pyib.py/manage and log in as user/password admin/admin
 Add a super administrator account with a strong password
 Log in as the new account and delete the default account